\v 16 ¬ЂMaaw…Фin wuyei …†aa, ta too, zii …†iligiti ti-loun anzanuiti ta too Ezipete yooi ta naћБ-nu…Уus…Ыiti faa zu,¬ї Mali…†ii ∆У…Фo…†…Ф GALAGI wooi …†ana.
