\v 2 ¬Ђ∆Кa  Лe, zunui, …†aa Лote G…Фge ma, Mes…Ыke ta Tu…Уale nuiti ta-…†undi…†i wolai, eћБ Mag…Фge yooi zu, GALA gooi wo daal…Ф…†…Фma,
